theorem Topology.frontier_eq_closure_inter_closureCompl {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X]
    (A : Set X) :
    frontier (A : Set X) = closure (A : Set X) ∩ closure (Aᶜ) := by
  -- Relate the frontier to an identity already established.
  have h :=
    (Topology.closure_inter_closureCompl_eq_closure_diff_interior (A := A)).symm
  simpa [frontier] using h

nonrec theorem Set.compl_compl {α : Type*} (s : Set α) : (sᶜ)ᶜ = s := by
  ext x
  by_cases hx : x ∈ s
  · simp [hx]
  · simp [hx]

theorem Topology.frontier_interior_eq_closureInterior_diff_interior
    {X : Type*} [TopologicalSpace X] (A : Set X) :
    frontier (interior A) = closure (interior A) \ interior A := by
  simp [frontier, interior_interior]
